content:
Insurance includes managed packages, unmanaged packages, and an Installation Assistant.

Managed Package: Required. Contains data model extensions, Apex Insurance services, templates, cards, Lightning components, product modeling components, and rating engine components.

Insurance Industries Extension Managed Package: Install in addition to the standard managed package if using Salesforce Financial Services Cloud. Contains Insurance components for use with Salesforce Financial Services Cloud.

Unmanaged Package: Contains Lightning record pages for product modeling and rating UI, as well as UIs for quotes, policies, and other objects. A new version is available for select releases.

Installation Assistant: An unmanaged package that walks you through installation and upgrade tasks. A new version is available for select releases.

Insurance FSC Unmanaged Package: Contains Digital Experience Site templates. To install, enable Digital Experience Sites first.

Get release summaries for major releases each winter, spring, and summer. Install minor releases by downloading the PDF and clicking the package link.
title: Salesforce Insurance Package Information
